text: Whipsaw is a 1935 American romantic crime drama movie directed by Sam Wood and starring Myrna Loy, Spencer Tracy, Harvey Stephens, William Harrigan, Robert Warwick, Clay Clement, Wade Boteler. It was distributed by Metro-Goldwyn- Mayer. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1935 drama movies Category:1935 romantic drama movies Category:1930s American crime drama movies Category:American romantic drama movies Category:MGM movies Category:Movies directed by Sam Wood
